choices.text:
Who is less bad: republicans, democrats, or libertarians?
Based on the data provided by https://www.isidewith.com/elections/2016-presidential-election/democrat-vs-republican and https://www.isidewith.com/political-quiz, it appears that Democrats are less bad than Republicans or Libertarians in terms of their stances on various issues such as healthcare, immigration, environment, taxes, education, etc.
